      "author": "Kunal1522",
      "description": "## Fix: completion bar display\n\nSession bars now fill the full row width at 100% completion. Previously, bar width was scaled against the longest session that day, so shorter sessions looked incomplete even at 100%.\n\n- 100% → full green bar\n- 90% → 90% green fill\n- 80% → 80% green fill\n\nDuration is still shown in the pill on the right.",
